  "title": "Software Engineer Intern",
  "description": "<h2>About Yuusoft and RouteVN</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Yuusoft Pte. Ltd. is a company incorporated in Singapore</li>\n  <li>Yuusoft Pte. Ltd. is the company that builds ands operates RouteVN</li>\n  <li>RouteVN is a dedicated platform for Visual Novels</li>\n  <li>Our <a href=\"https://routevn.com/blog/2025/01-to-fulfill-the-full-potential-of-visual-novels/\">mission</a> is to fulfil the full potential of Visual Novels</li>\n  <li>We build tools and technology to create, distribute and read Visual Novels</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a href=\"https://routevn.com/hiring/swe-intern#internship\">Internship</a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum duration of 3 months. Maximum duration of 6 months</li>\n  <li>Must be able to work <strong>full-time</strong> during the duration of the internship</li>\n  <li>This is a fully remote position. Applicants are welcome to apply from any timezone.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a href=\"https://routevn.com/hiring/swe-intern#job-description\">Job Description</a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Your mandate is to work to improve the product and building features for RouteVN</li>\n  <li>You will be working closely with <a href=\"https://han4wluc.com/\">@han4wluc (Luciano)</a> on a daily basis</li>\n  <li>You are expected to spend 70%+ of your time on engineering aspects and the remaining 30% on product aspects.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a href=\"https://routevn.com/hiring/swe-intern#what-an-ideal-candidate-looks-like\">What an ideal candidate looks like</a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>You have passion for Visual Novels and you share the RouteVN vision</li>\n  <li>You genuinely enjoy coding all day</li>\n  <li>You have a taste and high admiration for well crafted products</li>\n  <li>You are curious, fast learner and enjoy being exposed to new technologies</li>\n  <li>You are able to work independently take your own initiatives and responsibilities</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a href=\"https://routevn.com/hiring/swe-intern#tech-stack\">Tech stack</a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>We write almost all our code in Javascript and a little bit of Python</li>\n  <li>We build our own frameworks and libraries from scratch and open source all of it<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a href=\"https://routevn.com/hiring/swe-intern#application-and-selection-process\">Application and selection process</a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Application form submission</li>\n  <li>Video Interview</li>\n  <li>Take home assignment</li>\n  <li>Paid work trial</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Other notes</h1>\n<p>If you are not into Visual Novels, we have separate roles for other products as well</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Software Engineer - Devtools</li>\n  <li>Software Engineer - Edtech</li>\n</ul>",
